soap.subjective: Witnessed collapse in mall; bystander CPR ongoing; no prior complaints per wife on scene.
soap.objective: Unresponsive, apneic, pulseless. Initial rhythm VF. BVM with OPA. Multiple shocks delivered; epi given per ACLS. Post-ROSC vitals stable.
soap.assessment: Cardiac arrest due to VF; ROSC achieved; suspect acute coronary syndrome.
soap.plan: Post-ROSC care: 12-lead, IV fluids, oxygen, transport to PCI-capable center, alert ED.
